            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Remembered for good all those who donated and gave or will give for this holy
                    place either gold or silver or anything there is. Amen. Their portion is in this
                    holy place. Amen.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Damage to the letters is due to iconoclastic destruction of the adjacent
                    depiction of Daniel.</p>
            </div>
